title: LF Ranked team. Support & Jungle. Happy to be coached for team
body:
Hey guys. I have been playing for a while now. I am best with Support champs like Malphite and Janna or jungle with Elise or Maokai. Looking for a ranked team in need of either or both. Happy to be coached to fit style of play. I use Teamspeak and on for a fair few hours most weeknights and available weekends.

Thanks,

TheLowlyf

replies.body: Don't all reply at once! Flick a reply on here or add me on the LoL client. Ready and waiting!
